title: #exost  #hacking  #rccar  #rc   #workshop  with some #xr  #seriousgames  to learn with fun.
description: First edition of my workshop to play and learn how to hack an #exost #rc #rccar . We did some #soccer with the #rccars . Part of the workshop was to drive them with #xboxcontroller , #midi #keyboard , some #acrade #controler #button and #joystick . And give to other participant the training of fly easy #drone from #XR headset and a #seriousgame we created at the #globalgamejam last year. Lot's of fun.
